{"tid":2238354,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雞排妹信義區火辣裝「噴汗」吸睛 同居男室友意外現身","createTime":"2020-10-11T05:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T13:06:56.000Z","uid":147522,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6126d4f4cdfdc4d73dbaee0a4bd99363a40dc5bf","tid":2238354,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"女星雞排妹（鄭家純）今（13日）出席的直播平臺在信義區辦的活動，以一套性感的華麗禮服登場，雖然活動過程中炎熱，現場依舊粉絲眾多，早已汗如雨下的她更是熱情地與幸運粉絲進行「餵食秀」。另外，她也大方分享與友人在研發情趣用品，並表示親身投入研究「飛機杯」，對於產品非常有信心。<br />\n<br />\n雞排妹受訪除分享開發情趣用品外，被問到日前被拍到的「同居」男室友，她笑說對方今天擔任她的助理，人就在旁邊，絲毫不避諱，可見報導不影響兩人交情。雞排妹今代言全新的直播平臺，對直播向來有一套的她，未來的直播內容也備受粉絲期待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OX4i9pL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOX4i9pL.jpg&h=37db0b80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6r5PpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6r5PpL.jpg&h=69333e0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02502e4765bc47e2026226ada7db13443fcc33dc","tid":2238354,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"屌! 好想屌!"},{"pid":"18edb5b88d5d4e3a78f340c9d9ffedfa972161a6","tid":2238354,"uid":29929,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:26:57.000Z","msg":"點解佢得b都push 到咁宏偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c9fc9691594e6abe32ac9563ce9dd099f21626","tid":2238354,"uid":4562,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"個飛機杯係咪用自己做模"},{"pid":"c8b31524e0c3801832a82b1d78be21843072ff21","tid":2238354,"uid":362900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> J 了"},{"pid":"8af809e43f74c7f57b744661831c726f5c1ee14b","tid":2238354,"uid":112355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"好想做雞排妹室友<img src=\"/assets/fa